textBeforeTable: Allied commandos infiltrate the Bavarian mountain castle Schloss Adler to retrieve an American General possessing details of the Normandy invasion. After one of the commandos is found with a broken neck, it is apparent there is a double agent in their midst. One of the greatest war action films ever produced. Director: Brian G.
